---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  titulo="AWS Readiness Checklist — LRA Cloud Operations"
  descripcion="47 essential checks to audit your AWS infrastructure. Security, Reliability, Performance, Observability, Cost Optimization, and CI/CD."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 text-center" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A2540 0%, #1a3a5c 100%);">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider mb-6" style="background: rgba(30,111,255,0.2); color: #93c5fd;">
        Free tool
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
        AWS Readiness Checklist
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg mb-8" style="color: #94a3b8;">
        47 checks across 6 categories to audit your infrastructure before production.
      </p>
      <!-- Progress bar -->
      <div class="max-w-md mx-auto">
        <div class="flex justify-between text-sm mb-2" style="color: #94a3b8;">
          <span id="progress-label">0 of 47 completed</span>
          <span id="progress-pct">0%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="h-3 rounded-full" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
          <div id="progress-bar" class="h-3 rounded-full transition-all duration-500" style="background: #1E6FFF; width: 0%;"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Checklist -->
  <section class="py-12 px-4" style="background: #F8FAFF;">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8">

      <!-- Category: Security -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="px-6 py-4 flex items-center gap-3" style="background: #EEF4FF; border-bottom: 1px solid #C7D7FD;">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center" style="background: #1E6FFF;">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-bold text-base" style="color: #0A2540;">Security</h2>
            <p class="text-xs" style="color: #64748b;">10 checks</p>
          </div>
          <span class="ml-auto text-sm font-semibold" id="cat-security-count" style="color: #1E6FFF;">0/10</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="divide-y divide-gray-50" id="cat-security">
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="security">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">IAM: MFA enabled on root account and all IAM users</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Critical — The root account must never be used for routine operations.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="security">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">IAM: roles follow least privilege principle (no AdministratorAccess policies)</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Use IAM Access Analyzer to detect overly permissive access.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="security">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">S3: all buckets have Block Public Access enabled</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Enable at the account level to cover all current and future buckets.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="security">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">VPC: security groups without 0.0.0.0/0 rules on sensitive ports (22, 3306, 5432)</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Use a Bastion host or SSM Session Manager instead of direct SSH.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="security">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">Secrets Manager / Parameter Store for all credentials</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">No hardcoded secrets in code, EC2 environment variables, or Docker images.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="security">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">CloudTrail active in all regions with log file validation</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Store logs in a separate S3 bucket with MFA Delete enabled.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="security">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">GuardDuty enabled in all active regions</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">ML-based threat detection with no agents required.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="security">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">KMS: encryption at rest for RDS, S3 and EBS</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Use Customer Managed Keys (CMK) for greater rotation control.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="security">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">AWS Config enabled with compliance rules</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Recommended managed rules: restricted-ssh, s3-bucket-public-read-prohibited.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="security">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">ECR: Docker image vulnerability scanning enabled</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Enhanced scanning with Inspector for OS and application dependency CVEs.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Category: Reliability -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="px-6 py-4 flex items-center gap-3" style="background: #EEF4FF; border-bottom: 1px solid #C7D7FD;">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center" style="background: #1E6FFF;">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-bold text-base" style="color: #0A2540;">Reliability</h2>
            <p class="text-xs" style="color: #64748b;">10 checks</p>
          </div>
          <span class="ml-auto text-sm font-semibold" id="cat-reliability-count" style="color: #1E6FFF;">0/10</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="divide-y divide-gray-50" id="cat-reliability">
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="reliability">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">Multi-AZ on RDS and/or ElastiCache</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Automatic failover in case of availability zone failure.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="reliability">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">Auto Scaling Group configured in EC2/ECS with scaling policies</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Target Tracking with CPU/RequestCount. Minimum 2 instances in production.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="reliability">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">ALB/NLB configured with correct health checks</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Health check path returns 200 and verifies real connectivity (DB, cache).</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="reliability">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">Automatic RDS backups with retention ≥ 7 days</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Test restores periodically — a backup without a tested restore doesn't count.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="reliability">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">S3: versioning enabled on critical buckets</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Protects against accidental deletion and data corruption.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="reliability">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">Route 53 health checks and DNS failover configured</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Active-passive failover or latency-based routing for multi-region.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="reliability">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">ECS/EKS: deployment strategy with automatic rollback</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Rolling update or Blue/Green with circuit breaker in CodeDeploy.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="reliability">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">SQS/SNS to decouple critical services</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Dead Letter Queue configured with CloudWatch alarm.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="reliability">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">Terraform state in S3 + DynamoDB locking</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Remote state prevents conflicts in teams. Never local state in production.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="reliability">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">DR documented: RTO and RPO defined and tested</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Recovery runbook updated and accessible outside of AWS.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Category: Performance -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="px-6 py-4 flex items-center gap-3" style="background: #EEF4FF; border-bottom: 1px solid #C7D7FD;">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center" style="background: #1E6FFF;">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-bold text-base" style="color: #0A2540;">Performance</h2>
            <p class="text-xs" style="color: #64748b;">8 checks</p>
          </div>
          <span class="ml-auto text-sm font-semibold" id="cat-performance-count" style="color: #1E6FFF;">0/8</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="divide-y divide-gray-50" id="cat-performance">
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="performance">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">CloudFront CDN for static assets and frontend</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Correct Cache-Control headers. OAC instead of OAI for S3.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="performance">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">ElastiCache (Redis/Memcached) for frequent queries</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Cache sessions, DB results, and expensive API responses.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="performance">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">RDS: correct instance type + read replicas if read-intensive</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Performance Insights enabled to detect slow queries.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="performance">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">EC2/ECS: instance type adjusted to real load (not over-provisioned)</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Compute Optimizer analyzes historical metrics and recommends optimal sizing.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="performance">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">EBS: gp3 type (not gp2) on EC2 volumes</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">gp3 delivers better baseline performance at lower cost than gp2.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="performance">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">Lambda (if applicable): memory and reserved concurrency configured</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Lambda Power Tuning to find the optimal cost/performance balance.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="performance">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">VPC endpoints for AWS services (S3, DynamoDB, SQS)</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Avoid public internet traffic. Reduces latency and NAT cost.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="performance">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">Load testing executed before production</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Use k6, Locust, or AWS Distributed Load Testing. Document results.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Category: Observability -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="px-6 py-4 flex items-center gap-3" style="background: #EEF4FF; border-bottom: 1px solid #C7D7FD;">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center" style="background: #1E6FFF;">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-bold text-base" style="color: #0A2540;">Observability</h2>
            <p class="text-xs" style="color: #64748b;">8 checks</p>
          </div>
          <span class="ml-auto text-sm font-semibold" id="cat-observability-count" style="color: #1E6FFF;">0/8</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="divide-y divide-gray-50" id="cat-observability">
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="observability">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">CloudWatch Alarms on critical metrics (CPU, errors, latency)</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Alarms with SNS actions → email/PagerDuty/Slack configured.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="observability">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">Structured logs (JSON) with configured retention in CloudWatch Logs</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">30–90 days retention in prod. Logs without expiration accumulate unnecessary cost.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="observability">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">X-Ray or distributed tracing on critical services</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Identify bottlenecks and errors across microservices.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="observability">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">CloudWatch Dashboard with business and technical metrics</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">Combination of AWS metrics + application custom metrics.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="checklist-item px-6 py-4 flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors" data-cat="observability">
            <input type="checkbox" class="mt-0.5 w-4 h-4 rounded accent-blue-600 flex-shrink-0" />
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm font-medium" style="color: #0A2540;">Application health checks at /health or /ready endpoint</p>
              <p class="text-xs mt-0.5" style="color: #64748b;">The endpoint must verify real connectivity (DB, cache, external dependencies).</p>
            </div>
          </li>
